---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Section from "../components/Section.astro";
import PageHero from "../components/PageHero.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service | z4j"
  description="Terms of service for z4j, an open-source Python task queue control plane. AGPL-3.0 brain, Apache-2.0 agents. No CLA required. Self-hosted and self-managed."
  keywords={["z4j terms", "terms of service", "open source terms"]}
>
  <PageHero
    breadcrumb={[{ label: "Terms" }]}
    title="Terms of service"
    subtitle="Last updated: April 2026"
  />

  <Section>
    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-3xl text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] space-y-6">

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">Open-source software</h2>
        <p>z4j is open-source software. The brain is licensed under AGPL v3; agent packages are licensed under Apache 2.0. Your use of the software is governed by those licenses, not these terms.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">This website</h2>
        <p>z4j.com and z4j.dev are informational websites maintained by the z4j project. Content is provided as-is for documentation and marketing purposes.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">No warranty</h2>
        <p>z4j is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. See the AGPL v3 and Apache 2.0 license texts for the full disclaimer.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">Security</h2>
        <p>If you discover a security vulnerability, report it to <a href="mailto:security@z4j.com" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline">security@z4j.com</a>. Do not file a public issue. See our <a href="https://z4j.dev/security/disclosure/" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline">vulnerability disclosure policy</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">Commercial licensing</h2>
        <p>Commercial license terms are separate and provided on a per-organization basis. Contact <a href="mailto:licensing@z4j.com" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline">licensing@z4j.com</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">Changes</h2>
        <p>We may update these terms. Changes are committed to the public repository.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">Contact</h2>
        <p>General inquiries: <a href="mailto:hello@z4j.com" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline">hello@z4j.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>
